00:03.760 --> 00:05.720
BECKY: Hey, you're all dressed up.

00:05.760 --> 00:07.230
You going to court?

00:08.430 --> 00:09.980
Unlike you, people get dressed up

00:09.990 --> 00:13.840
for other reasons than trying
to beat a shoplifting charge.

00:13.850 --> 00:16.750
The saleswoman said I could
walk around in the shoes.

00:16.790 --> 00:19.880
I wanted to see how they
felt on the sidewalk.

00:19.980 --> 00:21.630
You're a criminal.

00:21.680 --> 00:23.880
I'm just trying to look
nice for work. That's all.

00:23.980 --> 00:26.110
That is so cute!

00:26.150 --> 00:28.750
You're trying to be a girl!

00:29.800 --> 00:31.899
This is obviously about her new boss.

00:31.900 --> 00:34.660
- [GASPS] You have a crush on your boss?
- Ooh!

00:34.680 --> 00:37.139
No, I'm just trying
to be a professional.

00:37.140 --> 00:38.920
God, all I did was put
on a little makeup.

00:39.020 --> 00:41.360
I heard the blow dryer.

00:41.780 --> 00:45.440
I was blowing dust out
of the smoke alarms.

00:45.480 --> 00:48.260
Nice try. They're all here!

00:48.320 --> 00:50.850
♪

00:50.890 --> 00:52.520
Do you ever worry that
some of the people

00:52.560 --> 00:54.520
in these mug shots might be innocent.

00:54.990 --> 00:56.880
Eh, people can think whatever they want.

00:56.900 --> 00:59.760
We're just reporting,
not passing judgment.

00:59.860 --> 01:01.900
Uh, the paper's called <i>Lock 'Em Up.</i>

01:01.930 --> 01:02.960
It's kind of judge-y.

01:02.970 --> 01:04.739
[LAUGHS]

01:04.760 --> 01:05.800
Ooh.

01:05.840 --> 01:07.500
This one's kind of hot.

01:07.540 --> 01:09.140
Let's put her on the front page.

01:09.240 --> 01:10.879
Oh, so that's what you're attracted to?

01:10.880 --> 01:12.240
Blondes with most of their teeth?

01:14.350 --> 01:15.960
I think you know exactly
the kind of woman

01:15.980 --> 01:17.040
I'm attracted to.

01:22.000 --> 01:23.440
[CLEARS THROAT]

